  "id": "nn_mmm88nl0_vmc0gtvlt",
  "title": "Network Security and Cryptography",
  "content": "\n\n<h1 data-end=\"250\" data-start=\"204\" data-section-id=\"1632p3g\">Cryptography Notes (Hinglish – Line by Line)</h1>\n<h3 data-end=\"287\" data-start=\"252\" data-section-id=\"1bkemz8\">1. Introduction to Cryptography</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"534\" data-start=\"288\">\n<li data-end=\"382\" data-start=\"288\" data-section-id=\"1x5gkto\">\n<p data-end=\"382\" data-start=\"290\">Cryptography ek <strong data-end=\"325\" data-start=\"306\">art aur science</strong> hai jo messages ko secure banane ke liye use hoti hai.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"461\" data-start=\"383\" data-section-id=\"1pi5s1v\">\n<p data-end=\"461\" data-start=\"385\">Iska main goal hai <strong data-end=\"458\" data-start=\"404\">information ko unauthorized logon se protect karna</strong>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"534\" data-start=\"462\" data-section-id=\"1f8dh1q\">\n<p data-end=\"534\" data-start=\"464\">Internet par data send karte time security bahut important hoti hai.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"539\" data-start=\"536\">\n<h3 data-end=\"558\" data-start=\"541\" data-section-id=\"j8rggt\">2. Plain Text</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"690\" data-start=\"559\">\n<li data-end=\"635\" data-start=\"559\" data-section-id=\"24ptai\">\n<p data-end=\"635\" data-start=\"561\"><strong data-end=\"575\" data-start=\"561\">Plain text</strong> wo original message hota hai jo sender bhejna chahta hai.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"690\" data-start=\"636\" data-section-id=\"ga6rdf\">\n<p data-end=\"690\" data-start=\"638\">Ye message <strong data-end=\"680\" data-start=\"649\">readable aur understandable</strong> hota hai.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-end=\"733\" data-start=\"692\">Example:<br data-end=\"703\" data-start=\"700\">\n<code data-end=\"710\" data-start=\"703\">HELLO</code> ya koi normal message.</p>\n<hr data-end=\"738\" data-start=\"735\">\n<h3 data-end=\"757\" data-start=\"740\" data-section-id=\"k5mwr8\">3. Encryption</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"959\" data-start=\"758\">\n<li data-end=\"838\" data-start=\"758\" data-section-id=\"8z49pj\">\n<p data-end=\"838\" data-start=\"760\"><strong data-end=\"774\" data-start=\"760\">Encryption</strong> ka matlab hai plain text ko <strong data-end=\"818\" data-start=\"803\">cipher text</strong> me convert karna.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"906\" data-start=\"839\" data-section-id=\"rxtsu1\">\n<p data-end=\"906\" data-start=\"841\">Is process me ek <strong data-end=\"890\" data-start=\"858\">encryption algorithm aur key</strong> use hoti hai.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"959\" data-start=\"907\" data-section-id=\"1dsfcsw\">\n<p data-end=\"959\" data-start=\"909\">Encryption ke baad message unreadable ho jata hai.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-end=\"1005\" data-start=\"961\">Example:<br data-end=\"972\" data-start=\"969\">\nHELLO → XGHTR (random coded form)</p>\n<hr data-end=\"1010\" data-start=\"1007\">\n<h3 data-end=\"1030\" data-start=\"1012\" data-section-id=\"1vnexes\">4. Cipher Text</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1187\" data-start=\"1031\">\n<li data-end=\"1078\" data-start=\"1031\" data-section-id=\"heapk1\">\n<p data-end=\"1078\" data-start=\"1033\"><strong data-end=\"1048\" data-start=\"1033\">Cipher text</strong> encrypted message hota hai.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1131\" data-start=\"1079\" data-section-id=\"16k4pdw\">\n<p data-end=\"1131\" data-start=\"1081\">Ye message <strong data-end=\"1128\" data-start=\"1092\">normal logon ko samajh nahi aata</strong>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1187\" data-start=\"1132\" data-section-id=\"b1skmo\">\n<p data-end=\"1187\" data-start=\"1134\">Sirf authorized receiver hi ise decode kar sakta hai.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"1192\" data-start=\"1189\">\n<h3 data-end=\"1211\" data-start=\"1194\" data-section-id=\"dok8qg\">5. Decryption</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1367\" data-start=\"1212\">\n<li data-end=\"1308\" data-start=\"1212\" data-section-id=\"jhwlww\">\n<p data-end=\"1308\" data-start=\"1214\"><strong data-end=\"1228\" data-start=\"1214\">Decryption</strong> cipher text ko wapas <strong data-end=\"1301\" data-start=\"1250\">original plain text me convert karne ki process</strong> hai.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1367\" data-start=\"1309\" data-section-id=\"zuuox5\">\n<p data-end=\"1367\" data-start=\"1311\">Iske liye <strong data-end=\"1353\" data-start=\"1321\">decryption algorithm aur key</strong> use hoti hai.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-end=\"1393\" data-start=\"1369\">Cipher Text → Plain Text</p>\n<hr data-end=\"1398\" data-start=\"1395\">\n<h3 data-end=\"1446\" data-start=\"1400\" data-section-id=\"19h248y\">6. Importance of Encryption and Decryption</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1698\" data-start=\"1447\">\n<li data-end=\"1498\" data-start=\"1447\" data-section-id=\"3x4xpp\">\n<p data-end=\"1498\" data-start=\"1449\">Internet par data ko <strong data-end=\"1495\" data-start=\"1470\">secure banane ke liye</strong>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1568\" data-start=\"1499\" data-section-id=\"73r9xi\">\n<p data-end=\"1568\" data-start=\"1501\">Hackers ya attackers se <strong data-end=\"1565\" data-start=\"1525\">information ko protect karne ke liye</strong>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1638\" data-start=\"1569\" data-section-id=\"1n1bnno\">\n<p data-end=\"1638\" data-start=\"1571\">Banking, WhatsApp messages, emails jaise systems me use hota hai.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1698\" data-start=\"1639\" data-section-id=\"1wrh4i8\">\n<p data-end=\"1698\" data-start=\"1641\">Sensitive data ko <strong data-end=\"1675\" data-start=\"1659\">confidential</strong> banaye rakhne ke liye.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"1703\" data-start=\"1700\">\n<h1 data-end=\"1728\" data-start=\"1705\" data-section-id=\"1hublaq\">Types of Cryptography</h1>\n<h2 data-end=\"1758\" data-start=\"1730\" data-section-id=\"27f94f\">1. Symmetric Cryptography</h2>\n<ul data-end=\"1947\" data-start=\"1759\">\n<li data-end=\"1833\" data-start=\"1759\" data-section-id=\"1oomicx\">\n<p data-end=\"1833\" data-start=\"1761\">Isme <strong data-end=\"1778\" data-start=\"1766\">same key</strong> encryption aur decryption dono ke liye use hoti hai.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1895\" data-start=\"1834\" data-section-id=\"jfmose\">\n<p data-end=\"1895\" data-start=\"1836\">Sender aur receiver ke paas <strong data-end=\"1883\" data-start=\"1864\">same secret key</strong> hoti hai.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1947\" data-start=\"1896\" data-section-id=\"t6u08s\">\n<p data-end=\"1947\" data-start=\"1898\">Isse <strong data-end=\"1931\" data-start=\"1903\">Private Key Cryptography</strong> bhi kehte hain.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-end=\"1957\" data-start=\"1949\">Example:</p>\n<ul data-end=\"2041\" data-start=\"1958\">\n<li data-end=\"1999\" data-start=\"1958\" data-section-id=\"1v0s7fg\">\n<p data-end=\"1999\" data-start=\"1960\">Sender same key se encrypt karta hai.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2041\" data-start=\"2000\" data-section-id=\"kpqyys\">\n<p data-end=\"2041\" data-start=\"2002\">Receiver same key se decrypt karta hai.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-end=\"2051\" data-start=\"2043\">Problem:</p>\n<ul data-end=\"2108\" data-start=\"2052\">\n<li data-end=\"2108\" data-start=\"2052\" data-section-id=\"1xzrrqa\">\n<p data-end=\"2108\" data-start=\"2054\">Agar key leak ho gayi to security khatam ho sakti hai.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2113\" data-start=\"2110\">\n<h2 data-end=\"2144\" data-start=\"2115\" data-section-id=\"7al0bx\">2. Asymmetric Cryptography</h2>\n<ul data-end=\"2187\" data-start=\"2145\">\n<li data-end=\"2187\" data-start=\"2145\" data-section-id=\"1rdgpu8\">\n<p data-end=\"2187\" data-start=\"2147\">Isme <strong data-end=\"2172\" data-start=\"2152\">2 different keys</strong> use hoti hain.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ol data-end=\"2225\" data-start=\"2189\">\n<li data-end=\"2206\" data-start=\"2189\" data-section-id=\"1qhvjws\">\n<p data-end=\"2206\" data-start=\"2192\"><strong data-end=\"2206\" data-start=\"2192\">Public Key</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2225\" data-start=\"2207\" data-section-id=\"f9okpv\">\n<p data-end=\"2225\" data-start=\"2210\"><strong data-end=\"2225\" data-start=\"2210\">Private Key</strong></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p data-end=\"2235\" data-start=\"2227\">Process:</p>\n<ul data-end=\"2312\" data-start=\"2236\">\n<li data-end=\"2274\" data-start=\"2236\" data-section-id=\"1wi4vrv\">\n<p data-end=\"2274\" data-start=\"2238\">Public key se encryption hota hai.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2312\" data-start=\"2275\" data-section-id=\"zkgy9p\">\n<p data-end=\"2312\" data-start=\"2277\">Private key se decryption hota hai.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-end=\"2362\" data-start=\"2314\">Isko <strong data-end=\"2346\" data-start=\"2319\">Public Key Cryptography</strong> bhi kehte hain.</p>\n<hr data-end=\"2367\" data-start=\"2364\">\n<h1 data-end=\"2389\" data-start=\"2369\" data-section-id=\"1vig1xr\">Encryption Schemes</h1>\n<p data-end=\"2462\" data-start=\"2391\">Encryption schemes me mainly 2 important security properties hoti hain.</p>\n<hr data-end=\"2467\" data-start=\"2464\">\n<h2 data-end=\"2497\" data-start=\"2469\" data-section-id=\"1k95my1\">1. Unconditional Security</h2>\n<ul data-end=\"2712\" data-start=\"2498\">\n<li data-end=\"2653\" data-start=\"2498\" data-section-id=\"1l96wo3\">\n<p data-end=\"2653\" data-start=\"2500\">Agar encryption scheme <strong data-end=\"2549\" data-start=\"2523\">unconditionally secure</strong> hai to attacker kitni bhi information le le,<br data-end=\"2597\" data-start=\"2594\">\nwo <strong data-end=\"2650\" data-start=\"2602\">original plain text determine nahi kar sakta</strong>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2712\" data-start=\"2654\" data-section-id=\"gv33n\">\n<p data-end=\"2712\" data-start=\"2656\">Isme security <strong data-end=\"2692\" data-start=\"2670\">mathematical proof</strong> se strong hoti hai.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-end=\"2729\" data-start=\"2714\">Simple meaning:</p>\n<ul data-end=\"2778\" data-start=\"2730\">\n<li data-end=\"2778\" data-start=\"2730\" data-section-id=\"xeqrat\">\n<p data-end=\"2778\" data-start=\"2732\">System theoretically <strong data-end=\"2768\" data-start=\"2753\">100% secure</strong> hota hai.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2783\" data-start=\"2780\">\n<h2 data-end=\"2813\" data-start=\"2785\" data-section-id=\"8e95fz\">2. Computational Security</h2>\n<ul data-end=\"2932\" data-start=\"2814\">\n<li data-end=\"2932\" data-start=\"2814\" data-section-id=\"1ras53c\">\n<p data-end=\"2932\" data-start=\"2816\">Agar encryption ko break karna <strong data-end=\"2881\" data-start=\"2847\">bahut zyada time aur resources</strong> leta hai to use computationally secure kehte hain.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-end=\"2968\" data-start=\"2934\">Ye 2 factors par depend karta hai:</p>\n<ol data-end=\"3042\" data-start=\"2970\">\n<li data-end=\"3010\" data-start=\"2970\" data-section-id=\"1xdjakt\">\n<p data-end=\"3010\" data-start=\"2973\"><strong data-end=\"3010\" data-start=\"2973\">Time required to break encryption</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"3042\" data-start=\"3011\" data-section-id=\"6qnkay\">\n<p data-end=\"3042\" data-start=\"3014\"><strong data-end=\"3042\" data-start=\"3014\">Amount of encrypted data</strong></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p data-end=\"3054\" data-start=\"3044\">Condition:</p>\n<ul data-end=\"3209\" data-start=\"3055\">\n<li data-end=\"3209\" data-start=\"3055\" data-section-id=\"12mjwbu\">\n<p data-end=\"3209\" data-start=\"3057\">Agar attacker ko encryption todne me information ke useful lifetime se <strong data-end=\"3152\" data-start=\"3128\">zyada time lagta hai</strong>,<br data-end=\"3156\" data-start=\"3153\">\nto system <strong data-end=\"3194\" data-start=\"3168\">computationally secure</strong> mana jata hai.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"3214\" data-start=\"3211\">\n<h1 data-end=\"3244\" data-start=\"3216\" data-section-id=\"lhz72k\">Definition of Cryptography</h1>\n<p data-end=\"3291\" data-start=\"3245\">Cryptography ek <strong data-end=\"3280\" data-start=\"3261\">art aur science</strong> hai jisme:</p>\n<ul data-end=\"3490\" data-start=\"3293\">\n<li data-end=\"3333\" data-start=\"3293\" data-section-id=\"d993yx\">\n<p data-end=\"3333\" data-start=\"3295\"><strong data-end=\"3328\" data-start=\"3295\">Readable message (plain text)</strong> ko</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"3396\" data-start=\"3334\" data-section-id=\"970333\">\n<p data-end=\"3396\" data-start=\"3336\"><strong data-end=\"3369\" data-start=\"3336\">Unreadable form (cipher text)</strong> me convert kiya jata hai</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"3490\" data-start=\"3397\" data-section-id=\"1hqumh4\">\n<p data-end=\"3490\" data-start=\"3399\">aur fir wapas <strong data-end=\"3430\" data-start=\"3413\">original form</strong> me convert kiya jata hai<br data-end=\"3458\" data-start=\"3455\">\ntaaki communication secure rahe.</p></li></ul>\n\n",
